    "detail": "<p>哈深18级本科生一枚，和许多同级的学生一样，为了准备就业，在深圳找到了实习，需要和学校请假。</p><p>而学校并不批准，并且通知全员无故缺课有可能无法参加考试。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e64b2522024fe08bf1795fd189718805_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"617\" data-rawheight=\"877\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"617\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e64b2522024fe08bf1795fd189718805_r.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c9c6408f56175cf66fc42935272d2df1_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"664\" data-rawheight=\"987\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"664\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c9c6408f56175cf66fc42935272d2df1_r.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3bb51c243fc0d8c8d509de114d283a12_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"548\" data-rawheight=\"961\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"548\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-3bb51c243fc0d8c8d509de114d283a12_r.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p>但实际上，学校方面是有相关的文件表明可以请假：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-841ca7445095058bcfd287ba96b086ee_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"828\" data-rawheight=\"710\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"828\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-841ca7445095058bcfd287ba96b086ee_r.jpg\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-65f1c90d64823972cb300324787ecdc6_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"828\" data-rawheight=\"517\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"828\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-65f1c90d64823972cb300324787ecdc6_r.jpg\"/></figure><p>不知道大家如何看待，我目前先和公司请假了。</p>",
